snippet.title: Diana and her Barbie car - Camping adventure
snippet.description:
Diana with her brother go Camping in their Power Wheels Barbie camper van! The children wanted to make a picnic themselves, but incredible events happen to them. Amazing Camping adventure with Barbie car!
